on some chores around here.

583
00:48:29,627 --> 00:48:32,129
You know, the best prize
that life can offer

584
00:48:32,171 --> 00:48:34,923
is working hard at work worth doing.

585
00:48:49,103 --> 00:48:50,312
Hey...

586
00:48:52,439 --> 00:48:54,733
