610
00:50:57,012 --> 00:51:00,682
So? My dad gets mad at me...
pretty much all the time.

611
00:51:00,724 --> 00:51:02,892
- He hits her.
- Oh.

612
00:51:02,934 --> 00:51:06,771
Some neighbor heard them
yelling so loud, they called the police.

613
00:51:06,854 --> 00:51:10,816
