- Can't. I got chores.

630
00:51:59,611 --> 00:52:02,405
- How about the next day?
- Sunday we go to church.

631
00:52:02,488 --> 00:52:04,449
- Can I come?
- You'd hate it.

632
00:52:04,490 --> 00:52:07,868
- No, I think it'd be cool.
