It's scary!

639
00:53:17,849 --> 00:53:20,185
It's nailing holes through your hands.

640
00:53:20,226 --> 00:53:23,771
It's 'cause we're all vile sinners.
God made Jesus die.

641
00:53:23,855 --> 00:53:26,607
