653
00:54:03,016 --> 00:54:05,810
Hey, Jess.
Give me a hand.

654
00:54:07,061 --> 00:54:08,896
Yeah. I'm coming.

655
00:54:10,731 --> 00:54:12,941
Get my drill out of the greenhouse.

656
00:54:30,749 --> 00:54:32,668
