663
00:55:08,367 --> 00:55:10,202
- Think!
- I put the drill down here.

664
00:55:10,286 --> 00:55:13,330
Damn it, the keys to the store
are on it, the register, all of it.

665
00:55:13,372 --> 00:55:16,291
