673
00:55:37,853 --> 00:55:40,563
and now he has to get
new keys made, and locks.

674
00:55:40,647 --> 00:55:42,190
May Belle?

675
00:55:42,273 --> 00:55:44,567
Please don't anyone get mad at me.

676
00:55:44,650 --> 00:55:46,902
- What?
- He...

677
00:55:46,944 --> 00:55:50,072
- I know where your dad's keys are.
- You do?

678
00:55:50,698 --> 00:55:53,367
You know the bells
we talked about making?

679
00:55:53,450 --> 00:55:56,620
Well, it was meant to be a surprise.

680
00:55:56,703 --> 00:55:58,538
All that clanking metal and junk.

681
00:55:58,622 --> 00:56:01,166
And... May Belle wanted to help.

682
00:56:01,249 --> 00:56:02,709
And you let her?

683
00:56:04,210 --> 00:56:06,546
Why did you tell me
you found them on the ground?

684
00:56:06,629 --> 00:56:09,090
- They were.
- On the ground in the greenhouse.

685
00:56:09,131 --> 00:56:11,508
What's the matter with you?
Dad wants to kill me.

686
00:56:11,550 --> 00:56:14,052
I was waiting for the right time.

687
00:56:16,471 --> 00:56:18,348
So you know where the keys are?

688
00:56:28,524 --> 00:56:29,733
See ya later.

689
00:56:32,319 --> 00:56:35,447
- Tell Mom I'll be home in a bit.
- Are you gonna tell Dad it was me?

690
00:56:35,530 --> 00:56:38,742
