707
00:58:27,091 --> 00:58:28,134
Run!

708
00:58:28,968 --> 00:58:30,719
Come on! Faster!

709
00:58:30,761 --> 00:58:33,555
Dead meat! Dead meat!

710
00:58:35,682 --> 00:58:36,892
Dead meat! Dead meat!

711
00:58:42,438 --> 00:58:43,981
Told you they were grenades.

712
00:58:51,989 --> 00:58:53,073
Jess!

713
00:58:53,157 --> 00:58:54,783
I got you, Leslie!

714
00:58:55,701 --> 00:58:56,827
I got you!

715
00:58:58,328 --> 00:59:00,163
